high_descs: Turn around and face the toaster.
Open the cabinet below the toaster and take the bottle out.
Turn around and face the refrigerator.
Open the fridge, place the bottle inside and chill it for 5 seconds. Then take the bottle back out.
Turn left and walk to the counter.
Place the bottle on the counter to the right of the fork.
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled bottle onto the counter.

high_descs: Turn around towards the toaster on the counter.
Open the cabinet below the toaster and get the bottle from it.
Turn around and walk towards the fridge.
Put the bottle to the left of the plate in the fridge for it to cool and then take it out of the fridge.
Place the bottle to the right of the fork on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place the cooled bottle on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right, move forward slightly, then turn right and face the toaster on the edge of the counter.
Open the cabinet door beneath the toaster, pick up the bottle of wine, and then close the cabinet door.
Turn around and move toward the refrigerator.

Open the refrigerator and place the bottle of wine to the left of the plate. Close the refrigerator, open the refrigerator, and pick up the bottle of wine to the left of the plate and close the refrigerator.
Turn left and move toward the dishwasher to the right of the sink.
Place the bottle of wine near the edge of the counter to the right of the fork.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled bottle of wine on the counter.
